            <div class="content">
                <div class="tagline">MAJU MARITIMKU JAYA INDONESIAKU</div>
                
                <div class="title-container">
                    <h1 class="main-title">MARINE SOLAR BOAT TEAM<br>ITS OFFICIAL WEBSITE</h1>

                    <div class="wave-animation-container">
                        <svg class="orange-wave" viewBox="0 0 400 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M 0 30 Q 200 50 400 10 Q 200 40 0 30 Z" fill="var(--bright-orange)"></path>
                            <path d="M 50 45 Q 200 60 350 25 Q 200 50 50 45 Z" fill="var(--bright-orange)" opacity="0.6"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="subtitle">Institut Teknologi Sepuluh Nopember Marine Solar Boat Team<br>The first solar powered boat team that represent ASEAN in Global Competition</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="frame bg-frame-2">
            <div class="overlay"></div>
            <div class="content">
                
                <div class="container text-center">
                    <div class="tagline mb-4 text-white">DISCOVER OUR JOURNEY</div>
                    
                    <div class="row justify-content-center">
                        <div class="col-11 col-md-8 col-lg-7">
                            <div class="video-frame">
                                <div class="ratio ratio-16x9">
                                    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-bmwsHbArSQ" title="MSBT Video Profile" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p class="subtitle mt-4">The ITS Marine Solar Boat Team (ITS MSBT) from the Sepuluh Nopember Institute of Technology is focused on building solar-powered vessels. The team is currently completing a vessel called the Jalapatih VI boat, featuring active hydrofoil innovation.</p>
                    
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="frame bg-frame-3" id="achievementFrame">
            <div class="overlay"></div>
            
            <div class="content center-content text-center">
                <h2 class="achievement-title">ACHIEVEMENTS</h2>
                <div class="achv-accent-line"></div>
                <p class="achv-center-text">
                    Pioneering the future of sustainable maritime technology and hydrofoil innovation on the global stage.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-container">
                
                <div class="achv-wrapper pos-1">
                    <div class="achv-card">
                        <div class="corner-badge">1st</div>
                        <h5 class="achv-name">JALAPATIH I</h5>
                        <img src="/assets/jp1.png" alt="Jalapatih I" class="achv-img">
                        <p class="achv-desc">First ASEAN solar boat presented in Global Competition (Dong Solar Energy Challenge 2014).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="achv-wrapper pos-2">
                    <div class="achv-card">
                        <div class="corner-badge">2nd</div>
                        <h5 class="achv-name">JALAPATIH II</h5>
                        <img src="/assets/jp2.png" alt="Jalapatih I" class="achv-img">
                        <p class="achv-desc">2nd Runner Up in Asia Dutch Solar Challenge.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="achv-wrapper pos-3">
                    <div class="achv-card">
                        <div class="corner-badge">3rd</div>
                        <h5 class="achv-name">JALAPATIH III</h5>
                        <img src="/assets/jp3-back.png" alt="Jalapatih I" class="achv-img">
                        <p class="achv-desc">3rd Position in Top Speed Category Solar Sport One.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="achv-wrapper pos-4">
                    <div class="achv-card">
                        <div class="corner-badge">1st</div>
                        <h5 class="achv-name">JALAPATIH IV</h5>
                        <img src="/assets/jp4.png" alt="Jalapatih I" class="achv-img">
                        <p class="achv-desc">First solar boat to use hydrofoil technology in Indonesia.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="achv-wrapper pos-5">
                    <div class="achv-card">
                        <div class="corner-badge">Mild</div>
                        <h5 class="achv-name">JALAPATIH V</h5>
                        <img src="/assets/jp5.png" alt="Jalapatih I" class="achv-img">
                        <p class="achv-desc">Used a planing hull to provide an angle of attack.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="frame bg-frame-4">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="container text-center">
                    
                    <div class="tagline text-white" style="margin-bottom: 60px;">SUPPORTED BY</div>
                    
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center align-items-center gap-4 gap-md-5">
                        
                        <img src="/assets/FIBERBOAT-LOGO.png" alt="Sponsor 1" class="sponsor-logo">
                        <img src="/assets/BBS-LOGO.png" alt="Sponsor 2" class="sponsor-logo">
                        <img src="/assets/DRAGONSHIP-LOGO.png" alt="Sponsor 3" class="sponsor-logo">
                        <img src="/assets/KUPPRUM-LOGO.png" alt="Sponsor 4" class="sponsor-logo">
                        <img src="/assets/JEMLA-LOGO.png" alt="Sponsor 5" class="sponsor-logo">
                        
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </div>

    <footer class="frame bg-frame-footer">
        <div class="content w-100">
            <div class="container text-start">
                <div class="row pt-5 justify-content-between">
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                        <h3 class="footer-heading">HEADQUARTERS</h3>
